rit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n            <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n              <td style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;padding: 20px;\">\n                \n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin: 0; padding: 0; font-size: 13px;\">\n                  Dear <t t-out=\"object.partner_id.name or 'Applicant'\"/>,\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  Thank you for your interest in joining the <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name or 'Our Company'\"/></b> team. We appreciate the time and effort you put into your application.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  <!-- Application Update -->\n                  Unfortunately, despite multiple attempts, we were unable to reach you. As a result, we had to mark your application as <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\">withdrawn due to non-response</b>.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  <!-- Reassurance -->\n                  We understand that circumstances may sometimes prevent timely communication. Please rest assured that this decision does not reflect the quality of your application or your professional abilities.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  <!-- Call to Action -->\n                  If you believe this was a misunderstanding or if you have updated contact information, please do not hesitate to reply to this email. We would be happy to revisit your application.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  <!-- Future Opportunities -->\n                  We will keep your resume on file and may reach out in the future regarding opportunities that align with your skills and experience.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  <!-- Closing -->\n                  We appreciate your understanding and wish you the best in your job search. We hope to have the opportunity to connect with you again.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  Best regards,<br/>\n                  The HR Team<br/>\n                  <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name or 'Our Company'\"/><br/>\n                  <a t-att-href=\"object.company_id.website\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;text-decoration: none; color: #374151;\">\n                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"/>\n                  </a>\n                </p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n",
